        <![CDATA[<h1>Windows配置codex</h1><p>作者：Curry-zhang（z13869291731@163.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="切换到-镜像-mirrored-网络模式">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%88%87%e6%8d%a2%e5%88%b0-%e9%95%9c%e5%83%8f-mirrored-%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%a8%a1%e5%bc%8f"></a>
<strong>切换到 “镜像 (Mirrored)” 网络模式</strong>
</h1><h2 id="1-在-windows-用户目录下例如-cusers你的用户名-创建或编辑文件-wslconfig-">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e5%9c%a8-windows-%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b7%e7%9b%ae%e5%bd%95%e4%b8%8b%e4%be%8b%e5%a6%82-cusers%e4%bd%a0%e7%9a%84%e7%94%a8%e6%88%b7%e5%90%8d-%e5%88%9b%e5%bb%ba%e6%88%96%e7%bc%96%e8%be%91%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6-wslconfig-"></a>
1. 在 Windows 用户目录下（例如 C:\Users\你的用户名\ ）创建或编辑文件 .wslconfig 。
</h2><h2 id="2-在文件中加入类似内容">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e5%9c%a8%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6%e4%b8%ad%e5%8a%a0%e5%85%a5%e7%b1%bb%e4%bc%bc%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9"></a>
2. 在文件中加入类似内容：
</h2><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">[</span>wsl2<span class="o">]</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">[</span>experimental<span class="o">]</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">networkingMode</span><span class="o">=</span>mirrored
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">autoProxy</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">true</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">dnsTunneling</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">true</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">firewall</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">true</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="3-在-powershell-或命令提示符中执行">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#3-%e5%9c%a8-powershell-%e6%88%96%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4%e6%8f%90%e7%a4%ba%e7%ac%a6%e4%b8%ad%e6%89%a7%e8%a1%8c"></a>
3. 在 PowerShell 或命令提示符中执行：
</h2><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl">wsl --shutdown
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="4-重新启动-wsl比如打开-ubuntu-等发行版">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#4-%e9%87%8d%e6%96%b0%e5%90%af%e5%8a%a8-wsl%e6%af%94%e5%a6%82%e6%89%93%e5%bc%80-ubuntu-%e7%ad%89%e5%8f%91%e8%a1%8c%e7%89%88"></a>
4. 重新启动 WSL（比如打开 Ubuntu 等发行版）。
</h2><h1 id="在wsl上安装codex">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9c%a8wsl%e4%b8%8a%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85codex"></a>
<strong>在wsl上安装codex</strong>
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 下载并安装 nvm：</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">curl -o- &lt;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.3/install.sh&gt; <span class="p">|</span> bash
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 代替重启 shell</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="se">\\</span>. <span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="nv">$HOME</span><span class="s2">/.nvm/nvm.sh&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 下载并安装 Node.js：</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">nvm install <span class="m">24</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 验证 Node.js 版本：</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">node -v <span class="c1"># Should print &#34;v24.11.1&#34;.</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># 验证 npm 版本：</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">npm -v <span class="c1"># Should print &#34;11.6.2&#34;.</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="安装codex">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85codex"></a>
安装codex
</h2><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="err">npm</span> <span class="err">i</span> <span class="err">-g</span> <span class="err">@openai/codex</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="在-wsl-模式下打开位于-windows-的文件夹">
